# Keep docker build contexts lean + deterministic. Applies to builds
# rooted at the repo (e.g. the credential-proxy multi-stage build).
.git/
.github/
.venv/
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/tests/
docs/
infra/
*.log
# Eval runtime caches — generated by running evals locally, NOT source. The
# control-plane image COPYs ``tools/eval`` (Dockerfile) for the eval worker;
# without these excludes a local longmem embedding cache (>1 GB) gets baked
# into the image and blows the build's disk. ``.gitignore`` already keeps them
# out of git, but ``.dockerignore`` governs the build context independently.
**/.longmem_cache/
eval-out/
